al data protection regulations."},{"pid":"6f9fd2e49804c741019930e249af5f8e6cc98511","tid":2321251,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c70beb965c77240b611691d69520eacac0c873","tid":2321251,"uid":263183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"佢套感官樂園好震憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4d787a0318209f928b68698ce71fb7ccde9254","tid":2321251,"uid":215794,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"張相咁似火火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8079216083a54270474150d70ae6dffe33796ba6","tid":2321251,"uid":4260,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"外媒報道韓片《聖殤》殿堂級導演金基德武肺併發症離世 終年59歲<br />\n<br />\n曾經憑韓片《聖殤》勇奪第69屆威尼斯影展金獅獎的59歲殿堂級導演金基德，根據韓國傳媒報道，據俄羅斯外電報道，身在當地的金基德在拉脫維亞因武肺漢炎而死亡。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外媒報道：「韓國著名電影導演金基德下午因武漢肺炎併發症去世。金基德從俄羅斯聖彼得堡經愛沙尼亞前往拉脫維亞。」 據相關人士透露，金基德在拉脫維亞置業並獲得永久居住權，而他在當地居住期間確診武漢肺炎，在接受治療期間因併發症加重而去世。而韓國外交部方面表示正在確認事實。<br />\n<br />\n最近金基德在俄羅斯、哈薩克斯坦等地展開了活動。去年他擔任了莫斯科國際電影節的委員會會長，今年亦有在哈薩克斯坦用俄語拍攝了電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/AWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FAWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a58b867e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FAWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ%2F&h=2064c06b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/AWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f86ba3d307daaf19cf2d356ca4ab7f5b266ce41b","tid":2321251,"uid":6436,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"嚟到12月都要整多單<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直數緊今年亞洲區有唔少名人過身，以為韓國會走得甩..."},{"pid":"1dd7d2e14a34842e28dcd015d1bc922a90f62f4e","tid":2321251,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a804fa47452eea862e74dfc2af4f5cc3dd692ec","tid":2321251,"uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"Mubi懷念緊 依然未有韓媒消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mubi/status/1337352114465550338?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmubi%2Fstatus%2F1337352114465550338%3Fs%3D21&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d6126790\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmubi%2Fstatus%2F1337352114465550338%3Fs%3D21&h=6eceda71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mubi/status/1337352114465550338?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6be273f9a082e58c86cb1e49e704bb36042032e4","tid":2321251,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"3cbc65e5e2a52db6c03b661e07fe89b5961d82d9","tid":2321251,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">CHINA VIRUS</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33ae39fd8087406218363b675f547f72d42aa38","tid":2321251,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gi