攝了電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/AWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FAWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a58b867e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FAWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ%2F&h=2064c06b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/AWJ5O72KRVEF7MNNK2XXQYZLGQ/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"火雲邪神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c57fe2f56796b694ed66d05fa2f4e19563ad36","tid":2321251,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"中共又殺咗人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2592fba92f68c2c68d315d1c4e47b6a810023cf","tid":2321251,"uid":28353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"母子<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdbf5917f4bdb6da54248c7b6a88999609b71e5","tid":2321251,"uid":197163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53b51ee76a168708e40164154c3988b672de1631","tid":2321251,"uid":81214,"like":87,"dislike":4,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"咁只會越嚟越多人憎支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"人地當普通流感，唔會理邊度係發源地，咪再FF啦"},{"pid":"e2dffac308953cca984a080f58a86d957dc4af0c","tid":2321251,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"天嫉英才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ed80c1b75ff8c19832de1c9df84c8e88